@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}

<head>
    <link href="~/Content/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body style="background-image: url('https://cdn.thecoolist.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Wild-African-elephant-in-the-savannah-Serengeti-National-Park.jpg'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover">
    <div style="background-color:lightblue">
        <div class="jumbotron" style="background-color:darkcyan">
            <h1>Feed A Child</h1>
            <p class="lead">Promoting SDG Goal 1 (No Poverty) and Goal 2 (Zero Hunger)</p>            
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                    <div id="imageCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-interval="5000"
                         data-ride="carousel" data-pause="hover" data-wrap="true">

                        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                            <li data-target="#imageCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                            <li data-target="#imageCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                            <li data-target="#imageCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                            <li data-target="#imageCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
                            <li data-target="#imageCarousel" data-slide-to="4"></li>
                        </ol>

                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="item active">
                                <img src="~/Images/feed_a_child.jpg" class="img-responsive img-rounded" height="500" width="800">
                                <div class="carousel-caption">
                                    <h3></h3>
                                    <p style="font-weight: bold; color:black;font-size:small">Feed a Child</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <img src="~/Images/feed1.png" class="img-responsive img-rounded" height="500" width="800">
                                <div class="carousel-caption">
                                    <h3></h3>
                                    <p style="font-weight: bold; color: black; font-size: small">Feeding community</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <img src="~/Images/feed2.png" class="img-responsive img-rounded" height="500" width="800">
                                <div class="carousel-caption">
                                    <h3></h3>
                                    <p style="font-weight: bold; color: black; font-size: small">Providing apples to local children</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <img src="~/Images/feed3.png" class="img-responsive img-rounded" height="500" width="800">
                                <div class="carousel-caption">
                                    <h3></h3>
                                    <p style="font-weight: bold; color: black; font-size: small">Providing clothes to local children</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <img src="~/Images/feed4.png" class="img-responsive img-rounded" height="500" width="800">
                                <div class="carousel-caption">
                                    <h3></h3>
                                    <p style="font-weight: bold; color: black; font-size: small">Happy children with their food</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <a href="#imageCarousel" class="carousel-control left" data-slide="prev">
                            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-hand-left"></span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#imageCarousel" class="carousel-control right" data-slide="next">
                            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-hand-right"></span>
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <br />
        <br />

        <div style="padding: 0px 60px">
            <p>Make a Difference by donating money, food, or clothing. Even the smallest contribution can change a life.</p>
            <p>
                The Non-profit organisation "Feed a Child" aims eradicate poverty by helping children in need. Thousands of children go to bed hungry with no knowledge of when
                they might find their next meal. While many others live their lives never knowing what it is like to be truely starving. We believe it is the duty of the
                fortunate to help the unfortunate. Only by taking a stand and contributing to a better tomorrow can a difference be made. It is your turn to give back and
                save a life.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>One can give in many ways, it is up to you as to whether you will make that choice.</p>
            <p>Donations are open for money, food, and clothing. Alternatively volunteers are always welcome - Sign up today!</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("Donation","Home")">Make Donation</a>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("Volunteer","Home")">Volunteer</a>
            <br />
            <br />
            <p><i>Note: All monetary donations go towards providing food and comfort to the children.</i></p>
            <br />
            <p>Visit <a href="https://feedachild.co.za/">Feed a Child</a> for more information.</p>
            <br />
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>

<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="~/Scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

